@stability: experimental
@since: 2026-02-14
@reviewed: 2026-04-30

Feature: Subscription Analytics
  "Records subscription lifecycle events into the analytics warehouse."

  Consumes:
    - Event: subscription.created
    - Event: subscription.cancelled

  Scenario (happy-path): Created event recorded
    Given a 'subscription.created' event arrives
    When the analytics consumer processes it
    Then a row is appended to the subscriptions_created warehouse table
